Comment: Reason for obsoletion: [This term was obsoleted because it does not represent a real process. While subarachnoid space is a valid anatomical structure, it is formed by the development of the structures that surround it.](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/QuickGO/term/GO:1903374)
Reason for obsoletion: gas homeostasis (GO:0033483) considered an unnecessary grouping by GO curators.

Reason for obsoletion: this term is a too generic of a category that goes beyond the realm of biological attributes. For example, the obsolete term could be applied to chemicals in environmental samples which is beyond the scope of OBA.

Reason for obsoletion: the label 'paired-pulse facilitation trait' of OBA:VT0002918 and the definition of the matching term http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/VT_0002918 do not agree with the logical definition in OBA. No appropriate GO process term exists to correct the logical definition at the time of the term obsoletion.
